    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Then Jesus said unto the chief priests,.... After he had wrought this miracle, and had quieted the mob, and restrained them from falling upon the apostles, and cutting them to pieces, which in all likelihood they would otherwise have done; he addressed himself to \"the chief priests\", who were members of the Jewish sanhedrim, and ",
        "children": []
