            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "And the elders which were come to him; which came along with Judas and the multitude, in order to see things done to their mind, and to animate both Judas and the soldiers and their officers, by their presence, lest they should come without him, as they had before done, John 7:45. ",
        "children": [
